{"type": "article", "id": 14719, "title": "餐盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-10T06:49:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000322yI0XNdY548UOKc6F.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是装面包的篮子，其实也可以做餐盘。黑色的卡纸折出像扇子一样的外形，放在圆形的木板上，像一个小型的雕塑，非常有质感。木板的中间事先空出一块卡住纸，再用一小块木头卡在其中稳定。将食物放在其中，这样打开时就很有惊喜之感。<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2015/09/08/dough-gazebo/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142208HEKPnzI7cWYO01fS.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142209CNZaWb59HEYf1UDK.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"692\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142209nu180bqfew3hx9GF.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"692\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422102qOeCfbYZgULVEtB.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}